==> the BASE in Hexadecimal is : 16
==> we can use only 15 digites : 0 to 15 or F
==> the maximal value in Hexadecimal system is : 15

==> we chage 10 to A 
         and 11 to B
         and 12 to C
         and 13 to D
         and 14 to E
         and 15 to F
to distinguish between Hexadecimal and Decimal
Ex: 
     215  is maby Hexadecimal or Decimal
  but 2F is for sure Hexadecimal

Q1 : convert those hexadecimal numbers to decimal

  12A4_16 ==> 4772
  1C35_16 ==> 7221
  100_16 ==> 256
  115C_16 ==> 4444

Q2 : convert those decimal numbers to hexadecimal

  4772 ==> 12A4
  7221 ==> 1C35
  256 ==> 100
  4444 ==> 115C

Q3 : convert those hexadecimal numbers to binary
  
  13B4 ==> 0001001110110100
  A5 ==> 10100101

Q4   : convert those hexadecimal numbers to binary

  17E.F6 ==> 101111110.1111011
  B2CA.6F8 ==> 1011001011001010.011011111
  
Q4   : convert those binary numbers to hexadecimal.

  11111001101.101100101 ==> 7CD.B28
  101010111100.0010011101 ==> ABC.274

Q7 : convert those Hexadecimal numbers to octal.
//convert to binary than convert to octal

  1BA.C77_16 ==> 110111010.110001110111 ==> 672.6167_8
